3-in-1 special design, three parts can be freely combined and used. Combining large capacity and great practicality, this tool cart is designed to meet your storage needs for different tools!
With stylish appearance and lockable design, the tool cabinet can be used in garages, warehouses, workshops, repair shops and other places, which is the best choice for storing all your tools!

The middle part is detachable, and the top box and bottom cabinet can also be used separately.  The top is solid enough that you can work directly on it, or it can be opened for additional storage area.  The hooks on the cart side are also convenient for hanging your frequently used tools.  The top box can be removed and inserted into the bottom for transport if desired, and you can store it in garage corner or car trunk.  So the tool cart will provide with large storage space without taking up too much space.
[Premium Materials] - Our rolling tool box is made of high quality cold-rolled steel, the structure is strong and stable, ensuring maximum durability.  The surface of the cart is carefully polished and powder coated, easy to clean, and excellent in wear resistance and rust resistance.  The drawers use ball bearings for smoother opening and closing. The tool cabinet with wheels is suitable for garage, warehouse, workshop, repair shop and other places, widely used in gardening and auto maintenance.
[Storage Organizer] - Larger storage design, free combination and disassembly, easy to move, comes with lock to protect tools, with excellent functionality, the rolling tool chest will be an ideal choice for workshop storage!  And this tool chest looks so exquisite that it even fits perfectly as a piece of furniture at home.  (Please note that only the top box can be locked.)
